{"tid":499850,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大陸人真係好無【禮】","createTime":"2017-12-15T09:10:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-15T12:00:41.000Z","uid":146453,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"939f09c2d8123103f0705ee7e8d962faa5256aa4","tid":499850,"uid":146453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T09:10:06.000Z","msg":"連上下有別 尊卑有序都唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n岩岩小弟喺港鐵車廂入面，太子站有兩個人企左起身落車，姐係吉左兩個位，身邊有個學生哥坐左其中一個，果陣時我心入面仲笑鳩佢係廢青，話口未完，有兩個大陸人拖曬行李咁衝左入黎，一個用9秒9的速度坐底另外一個位，咁岩又有一個老人入左黎，凳都未暖個廢青即刻讓坐，令我另眼相看<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最on9係個學生哥一起身，坐左係道果個大陸人即刻叫佢嘅同胞過黎坐，心諗成個老人企係你面前你唔識讓坐之餘，仲唔比人地坐？"},{"pid":"f7855212228d97fd9cbba603849261c3230e5c7b","tid":499850,"uid":135340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T09:12:29.000Z","msg":"結果邊個坐咗？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10f1193dae2a04b4762258b5d5ef03557701769d","tid":499850,"uid":146453,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T09:14:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>結果邊個坐咗？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n老人都唔執輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 都幾爽手就坐左"},{"pid":"0c1b0df8aabdfb765e93cb178a1ee64e87426300","tid":499850,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T09:15:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ac6842d258e0ed31cf6448eca59d595ab0d48b54","tid":499850,"uid":146453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T09:17:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>老人想坐自然會出聲嫁啦。愛都要講出口啦，唔覺大陸人錯</blockquote><br />\n我都覺得讓坐係美德，唔可以比人道德綁架<br />\n但係ching 宜家係搶位坐wo"},{"pid":"80b4de16e3a9997bd4a4318a4b69a7eb9072da21","tid":499850,"uid":135340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T11:57:42.000Z","msg":"其實返大陸好多時都會見到d人會自動自覺讓關愛坐....係咪黎親香港個d素質特別低<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06b3bdf6a1934275739703a341b312526b085628","tid":499850,"uid":56432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T12:00:41.000Z","msg":"大陸喱個個黎香港都居高臨下心態啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}